articles.title: Ambassador Carlson Highlights Longstanding Friendship in Visit to Zamboanga City - US Embassy in Philippines
articles.description: Manila, October 28, 2022—On October 28, U.S. Ambassador to the Philippines MaryKay Carlson visited Zamboanga City to address local university students and meet with key leaders to reaffirm the longstanding friendship between Americans and Filipinos.
articles.content:
U.S. Ambassador MaryKay Carlson pays a courtesy call on Zamboanga City Mayor John Dalipe.
